      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.2zjfszFAX3NdZefF]{Stewards Stalwart}</p>\n<p>When you take damage from a significant enemy while you still have Stamina Points, as a reaction you can reduce the damage you take by an amount equal to your level plus your key ability modifier. You can’t use this feature if you’re unaware of the enemy when the attack hits you or if you’re @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Flat-Footed} against the attack at the time. Once you benefit from this feature, you can’t benefit from it again until you take a 10-minute rest to recover Stamina Points.</p>"
